  "syntaxRefTitle": "DrewMark Syntax Reference",
  "syntaxRefLines": [
    "> #### Headings",
    "> [-< ref: headings >-]",
    "> | \\# Heading 1 | h1 |",
    "> | \\## Heading 2 | h2 |",
    "> | \\### Heading 3 | h3 |",
    "> | \\#### Heading 4 | h4 |",
    "> | \\##### Heading 5 | h5 |",
    "> | \\###### Heading 6 | h6 |",
    "",
    "> #### Text-decors",
    "> [-< ref: text-decors >-]",
    "> | \\**bold\\** | **bold** | [-[ ref: bold strong ]-]",
    "> | \\%%italic\\%% | %%italic%% | [-[ ref: italic em ]-]",
    "> | \\__underline\\__ | __underline__ | [-[ ref: underline ins ]-]",
    "> | \\~~strike\\~~ | ~~strike~~ | [-[ ref: strike del ]-]",
    "> | \\!!highlight\\!! | !!highlight!! | [-[ ref: highlight mark ]-]",
    "> | \\^^superscript\\^^ | X^^2^^ | [-[ ref: sup ]-]",
    "> | \\<<subscript\\>> | H<<2>>O | [-[ ref: sub ]-]",
    "> | \\@@small text\\@@ | @@small text@@ | [-[ ref: small ]-]",
    "> | \\{{word^annotation\\}} | {{word^annotation}} | [-[ ref: annotation`/`ruby ]-]",
    "",
    "> #### Codes",
    "> [-< ref: codes >-]",
    "> | \\`Javascript\\` | inline code | [-[ ref: code-inline ]-]",
    "> | \\`\\`\\`\\nJavascript\\n\\`\\`\\` | code block | [-[ ref: code-block ]-]",
    "",
    "> #### Lists",
    "> [-< ref: lists >-]",
    "> | + unordered  | ● disc | [-[ ref: lists-unordered ul-disc ]-]",
    "> | - unordered  | ○ circle | [-[ ref: lists-unordered ul-circle ]-]",
    "> | * unordered  | ■ square | [-[ ref: lists-unordered ul-square ]-]",
    "> | 1. ordered  | 1. Arabic numerals | [-[ ref: lists-ordered ol-1 ]-]",
    "> | i. ordered  | i. Roman numerals (lower case) | [-[ ref: lists-ordered ol-i ]-]",
    "> | I. ordered  | I. Roman numerals (upper case) | [-[ ref: lists-ordered ol-I ]-]",
    "> | a. ordered  | a. Latin letter (lower case) | [-[ ref: lists-ordered ol-a ]-]",
    "> | A. ordered  | A. Latin letter (upper case) | [-[ ref: lists-ordered ol-A ]-]",
    "> | +*+ task  | ✅ done | [-[ ref: lists-task task-done ]-]",
    "> | -*- task  | ☐ undone | [-[ ref: lists-task task-undone ]-]",
    "",
    "> #### Table",
    "> [-< ref: table >-]",
    "> \\| thead 1 | thead 2 |",
    "> \\|====|====| ← 【separator row】",
    "> \\| tbody 1 | tbody 2 |",
    "> \\|====|====| ← 【separator row】",
    "> \\| tfoot 1 | tfoot 2 |",
    "",
    "> #### Embeds",
    "> [-< ref: embeds >-]",
    "> | \\(title){URL}  | link | [-[ ref: link a ]-]",
    "> | !\\(alt){URL}  | image | [-[ ref: image img ]-]",
    "> | !\\!!\\n\\! figure caption\\n!\\(alt){URL}\\n!\\!! | figure block | [-[ ref: figure-block figure ]-]",
    "> | ~\\(){URL\\|media type} \\ | audio | [-[ ref: audio ]-]",
    "> | $\\(){URL\\|media type}  \\| video | [-[ ref: video ]-]",
    "",
    "> #### Quotes",
    "> [-< ref: quotes >-]",
    "> | \\>>quotation\\<< | inline quote | [-[ ref: quote-inline ]-]",
    "> | > level 1\\n>> level 2 | quote block | [-[ ref: quote-block ]-]",
    "",
    "> #### Descs",
    "> [-< ref: descs >-]",
    "> | ;;term::description;; | description list | [-[ ref: deflist dl ]-]",
    "> | ;;;\\nany syntax\\n;;; | details | [-[ ref: details ]-]",
    "",
    "> #### Misc",
    "> [-< ref: misc >-]",
    "> | ((value//max)) | progress | [-[ ref: progress ]-]",
    "> | -\\-- | horizontal rule| [-[ ref: hr ]-]",
    "> | :\\:smile:\\: | emoji 😄 | [-[ enable: emoji ]-]",
    "> | {{{\\nCSS\\n}}} | style block | [-[ enable: style ]-]",
    "",
    "> #### Global Attrs",
    "> [-< ref: attrs >-]",
    "> | [A\\[ center ]A] | align | [-[ ref: attr-align ]-]",
    "> | [C\\[ class ]C] | class | [-[ ref: attr-class ]-]",
    "> | [D\\[ rtl ]D] | dir | [-[ ref: attr-dir ]-]",
    "> | [I\\[ id ]I] | id | [-[ ref: attr-id ]-]",
    "> | [L\\[ en ]L] | lang | [-[ ref: attr-lang ]-]",
    "> | [T\\[ title ]T] | title | [-[ ref: attr-title ]-]",
    "> | [-\\[ key: value ]-] | data-* | [-[ ref: attr-data ]-]",
    "",
    "> #### Dedicated Attrs",
    "> | __**!**__1. ordered | **reversed** for __<ol>__ |",
    "> | \\| cell __**&<integer>&**__ \\| | **colspan** for __<td>__ |",
    "> | \\| cell __**&/integer/&**__ \\| | **rowspan** for __<td>__ |",
    "> | ()\\{URL__**=>target**__} | **target** for __<a>__ |",
    "> | !( __**[W\\|H]**__ )\\{URL}\\n$( __**[W\\|H]**__ )\\{URL\\|media type} | **width** and **height** for __<img>__ and __<video>__ |",
    "> | ~( __**_**__ __**&**__ __**@**__ __**!**__ )\\{URL\\|media type}\\n$( __**_**__ __**&**__ __**@**__ __**!**__ )\\{URL\\|media type} | varies attrs for __<audio>__ and __<video>__ |",
    "> | $(__**{Poster}**__)\\{URL\\|media type} | **poster** for __<video>__ |",
    "> | >\\>quotes__**<=URL**__<\\<\\n\\> quotes__**<=URL**__ | **cite** for __<q>__ and __<blockquote>__ |",
    "> | ;;;\\nany syntax\\n;;;__**>**__ | **open** for __<detail>__ |",
    ""
  ]
}